##The old man who watched the sunset with the doctor is leaving the hospital

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Li Jiawei is a reporter for the paper

The 87-year-old man who watched the sun set with his doctor a few days ago has continued to get better. Previously on "Best Picture today, " we found the doctor

On March 12, the _ paper _ reporter learned of the news from the Hubei medical team supported by Shanghai Zhongshan Hospital. Liu Kai, a member of the medical team, said the old man's condition has improved significantly in all aspects. Recently, medical staff are strengthening the old man's rehabilitation exercise. The old man is expected to be discharged from the hospital in a week or so.

Zhu Wenbo, Video Editor: Zhou Yan, Source: Relevant Person Responsibility Editor: Zhou Qi

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
And the doctor watching the sunset, Mr. 87 turned negative. Zhongshan Hospital affiliated to Fudan University

Earlier, on March 5, Liu Kai stopped while escorting the 87 year old man to a CT scan at the East Hospital of the Wuhan University People's Hospital, where he had been hospitalized for nearly a month, to watch a long lost sunset.

The two figures, the patient and the doctor, were captured in the setting sun and moved countless netizens.
